Text: SANTA ROSA, Calif., Sept. 25, 2019 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Luther Burbank Corporation (the Company) (NASDAQ: LBC), the holding company for Luther Burbank Savings (the Bank), announced this week that it was awarded a $200,000 grant by FHLBank San Francisco (FHLBank) to benefit the Sonoma County Community Development Commission (CDC).
